content: A Psalm of Complaint and of Praise.
To the Chief Musician. A Psalm of David.
Incline Your ear to me, deliver me quickly;
And a strong fortress to save me.
Yes, You are my rock and my fortress;
For Your nameâ€™s sake You will lead me and guide me.
You will draw me out of the net that they have secretly laid for me,
For You are my strength  my stronghold.
Into Your hand I commit my spirit;
You have redeemed me, O , the God of truth  faithfulness.
